changelogs:
Version 1

  • Initial release.

Version 2

  • Fixed missing default trainable=False.
  • Fixed broken regularization_losses.

Version 3

  • Provides proper names for variables*comma* fixing crash in Model.save() (GitHub issue #287).

Version 4

  • Adds back missing update ops for batch norm that were lost in version 3*comma* (GitHub issue #304).
